---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Bookkeeping West Hollywood — Projexions"
  description="Monthly bookkeeping services for small businesses, agencies, and e-commerce sellers. Based in West Hollywood, serving clients nationwide."
  currentPath="/bookkeeping-west-hollywood"
>
  <div class="page-container">
    <h1 class="serif-heading text-4xl font-semibold mb-4 text-center">Monthly Bookkeeping</h1>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 text-center" style="color: var(--text-gray);">Based in West Hollywood · Serving clients nationwide</p>

    <div class="services-card">
      <div class="prose-content">
        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Orderly Books, Month After Month</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          For businesses that need reliable, ongoing bookkeeping—not just cleanup when things fall apart.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
          Projexions provides monthly bookkeeping services that keep your records accurate, organized, and ready for reporting, tax filing, or CPA review at any time.
        </p>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <h2 class="section-title text-center">What's Included</h2>

        <ul class="resource-list text-lg mb-6">
          <li>Bank and credit card reconciliation</li>
          <li>Expense categorization and organization</li>
          <li>Accounts payable and receivable tracking</li>
          <li>Payroll recording</li>
          <li>Stripe, Shopify, and payment processor reconciliation</li>
          <li>Monthly financial reports</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
          Services are tailored to what your business actually needs. No unnecessary add-ons.
        </p>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Who This Is For</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Small businesses, solo operators, agencies, and e-commerce sellers who want their books handled consistently—so they can focus on running their business.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
          If you've cleaned up your books and want to keep them that way, or if you're ready to hand off bookkeeping entirely, this is a good fit.
        </p>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Pricing</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Monthly pricing is based on transaction volume, complexity, and the specific services your business needs.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
          Start with a conversation to determine scope and fit.
        </p>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Get Started</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Reach out to discuss your bookkeeping needs and see if monthly support is the right fit.
        </p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Contact</a>
        </div>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Scope & Boundaries</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Projexions provides bookkeeping services—not tax advice, tax filing, or CPA services.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Work is scoped individually. No guarantees of outcomes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .services-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--ui-gray);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    max-width: 750px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .section-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ui-gray);
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
  }

  .section-cta {
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
